{"tid":1677600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警不停截查　質疑 NOW 攝影師記者證「寫住 PCCW 嘅？」","createTime":"2019-10-27T08:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T10:10:10.000Z","uid":38954,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11619a617a5a9a6977adb89056a64630a7b169df","tid":1677600,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:00:37.000Z","msg":"有網民發起今午 3 時在尖沙咀梳士巴利花園舉行「追究警暴、連繫穆斯林、守護公眾、與記者同行」和平集會。集會未開始，已有大批防暴警察在場戒備，截查在場人士。一名在場拍攝的 NOW 新聞台攝影師被警員要求出展身分證，警察質疑其員工證為何寫有「PCCW」（電訊盈科）字眼。<br />\n<br />\n當時 NOW 新聞台攝影師穿上反光衣，胸前掛上記者證，一名用毛巾蒙臉的警員，質疑攝影師的記者證「寫住 PCCW 嘅？」攝影師及另一穿上 NOW 新聞台字樣反光衣的記者連忙解釋，「NOW 囉，PCCW 即係。」<br />\n<br />\nNow TV 是香港的收費電視台，由電訊盈科全資擁有的電訊盈科媒體負責經營。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿蛇岩岩由大陸落黎嗎"},{"pid":"d6c4f928308e49f21d5bc949aa9f79555204165c","tid":1677600,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb48739bb0cab7660b80c867cda06c6a02a71d2","tid":1677600,"uid":69741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"d狗上下常識堂啦"},{"pid":"27ac460b644aacc5ca7212a151bd6d70ae7bde1e","tid":1677600,"uid":11563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"柒撚到笑"},{"pid":"d82205f30cfbc73fa08767ff5823c2f485991ebc","tid":1677600,"uid":275477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"又係帽警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8188c97fc368cd9cbf218fa0f5cc083d10c103f3","tid":1677600,"uid":238369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji